ygData.messageBody:
Try going to Freeport Paladin's guild and talk to the Guild Master and his
assitants (upstairs in the back part, go right at entrance). He will give
you soem basic quest as well as the guy in the yard out back. The guy in the
yard is important to see before you get too high in level, and you may need
someone to help you with that one.
